special_notes: State does not use letter 'O', only number '0'

Full rules: Does not use the Letter O on their standard license plates. Both the Letter O and Number Zero 0 are used on our Specialty Tags and Temporary Operating Permits. *FLAT designated plates are printed, not pressed.
